Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Section: libs
Homepage: https://github.com/airockchip/rknn-toolkit2

Package: librknnrt
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libc6, libstdc++6, libgcc-s1
Description: Rockchip RKNN NPU runtime (prebuilt)
 Prebuilt Rockchip RKNN runtime library (librknnrt.so) from rknpu2. The NPU
 inference runtime that applications link against.

Package: librknnrt-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: arm64
Depends: librknnrt (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Rockchip RKNN NPU runtime — development files
 RKNN headers (rknn_api.h, rknn_custom_op.h, rknn_matmul_api.h) and pkg-config
 (rknn) for building against librknnrt.

Package: rknn-server
Architecture: arm64
Depends: librknnrt (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Rockchip RKNN NPU server daemon
 The rknn_server NPU proxy daemon + systemd service (rknn-server.service),
 used to connect rknn-toolkit2 on a host to the on-device NPU runtime.
